<CaseStudy slug="operation-hired">
  <p class="lead reveal">I needed to run a serious job search, so I built the system I'd roll out to a team. Not a spreadsheet and not a folder of bookmarks: a pipeline that pulls postings in, scores them, drafts the application, and keeps a record of every send. The point was never the software. The point was to make one person move like a staffed function, without losing the judgment that makes the work any good.</p>

